OL,5,G1245 The Art of Racing in the Rain
OL,6,     F(2019) Touching comedy-drama. An
OL,7,     Fageing golden retriever (voiced by
OL,8,     FKevin Costner) tells the story of
OL,9,     Fhis life with his best pal, a
OL,10,     Fbudding Formula 1 driver.
OL,11,G1455 Sea Wife
OL,12,     F(1957) Offbeat melodrama starring
OL,13,     FRichard Burton (as an RAF
OL,14,     Fofficer), Joan Collins (as a nun),
OL,15,     FBasil Sydney and Cy Grant, who end
OL,16,     Fup on a life raft together after
OL,17,     Ftheir ship is torpedoed.
